	<h4 class="c-issue-toc__article-title" id="2120"><a href="/en/archive/empathetic-images/encountering-others-through-graphic-narrative">Encountering Others through Graphic Narrative. Layers of Empathy in Hanneriina Moisseinen’s "The Isthmus"</a></h4>
	<h5 class="c-issue-toc__article-authors"><!--Authors:--><a href="/en/bio?id=2122">Aura Nikkilä</a>, <a href="/en/bio?id=2123">Anna Vuorinne</a></h5>
	
				<a class="c-issue-toc__article-collapse-btn" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseDoi2120" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseSummary2120" data-lexicon-show="show" data-lexicon-hide="hide">
