	<h4 class="c-issue-toc__article-title" id="2171"><a href="/en/archive/empathetic-images/civic-voyeurism">Civic Voyeurism. Józef Robakowski’s Aerial Views of the Commons</a></h4>
	<h5 class="c-issue-toc__article-authors"><!--Author:--><a href="/en/bio?id=2172">Eliza Rose </a></h5>
	
				<a class="c-issue-toc__article-collapse-btn" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseDoi2171" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseSummary2171" data-lexicon-show="show" data-lexicon-hide="hide">
