	<h4 class="c-issue-toc__article-title" id="2187"><a href="/en/archive/empathetic-images/nurse-i-want-my-mummy">“Nurse! I Want My Mummy!”. Empathy as Methodology in the Documentary Film "A Two-Year-Old Goes to Hospital" (1952)</a></h4>
	<h5 class="c-issue-toc__article-authors"><!--Author:--><a href="/en/bio?id=2186">Justyna Wierzchowska</a></h5>
	
				<a class="c-issue-toc__article-collapse-btn" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseDoi2187" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseSummary2187" data-lexicon-show="show" data-lexicon-hide="hide">
