	<h4 class="c-issue-toc__article-title" id="2145"><a href="/pl/archiwum/26-empatyczne-obrazy/teoria-quasi-obiektu">Theory of the Quasi-Object</a></h4>
	<h5 class="c-issue-toc__article-authors"><!--Authors:--><a href="/en/bio?id=2143">Michel Serres</a></h5>
	
				<a class="c-issue-toc__article-collapse-btn" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseDoi2145" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseSummary2145" data-lexicon-show="show" data-lexicon-hide="hide">
